  "en|Exercise: Luna started a game with her classmates. Look at the card played by her partner in North. Which card do you advise Luna, sitting South, to play? Only the best card in Luna's hand is clickable. Press the announced number key to play it, listen to the rule, then continue": "5f6d9ea7a9a5ab3b.mp3",
