  "en|Lesson 4: the Library of Final Lessons. Here, one player lays their cards face up on the table: this player is called the dummy, l'endormi, the sleeping one. Their partner becomes the pilot of the team and decides which cards both of them play. If Luna succeeds, she collects the last potion of the grimoire: the Dummy Potion. Ready to help her? Press 1 to begin": "14fe499cdc7f37d2.mp3",
